{% comment %}
  GK Gristle King landing — 2. Problem → solution story
  The "Gristle Lowdown" letter, lifted from Greg's backline email (the
  campaign that performed well): the problem (questionable backline,
  borrowed amps) agitated in Greg's own voice, then the two-circuit answer
  as point cards, then the bridge to Tim Jauernig. All copy is editable in
  the theme editor.
{% endcomment %}

<div class="gkl">
  {%- if section.settings.show_top_divider -%}
    <div class="gkl-divider" aria-hidden="true"><hr></div>
  {%- endif -%}

  <section class="gkl-problem">
    <div class="gkl-wrap gkl-wrap--wide">
      <div class="gkl-section-head">
        {%- if section.settings.eyebrow != blank -%}
          <p class="gkl-eyebrow">{{ section.settings.eyebrow | escape }}</p>
        {%- endif -%}
        {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
          <h2 class="gkl-h2">{{ section.settings.heading | escape }}</h2>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>

      <div class="gkl-problem__grid">
        <div class="gkl-problem__photoCol">
          {%- if section.settings.image != blank -%}
            <div class="gkl-problem__photoFrame">
              {{
                section.settings.image
                | image_url: width: 1000
                | image_tag:
                  loading: 'lazy',
                  sizes: '(min-width: 750px) 42vw, 100vw',
                  widths: '400, 600, 800, 1000',
                  alt: section.settings.image.alt | default: 'Greg Koch'
              }}
            </div>
            {%- if section.settings.caption != blank -%}
              <p class="gkl-problem__caption">{{ section.settings.caption | escape }}</p>
            {%- endif -%}
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="gkl-problem__body">{{ section.settings.body }}</div>
          {%- if section.settings.signature != blank -%}
            <p class="gkl-problem__sig">{{ section.settings.signature | escape }}</p>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      </div>

      {%- if section.blocks.size > 0 -%}
        <div class="gkl-problem__points">
          {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
            <div class="gkl-point" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
              <i class="ti {{ block.settings.icon | escape }}" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <h3 class="gkl-point__title">{{ block.settings.title | escape }}</h3>
              <p class="gkl-point__text">{{ block.settings.text | escape }}</p>
            </div>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if section.settings.outro != blank -%}
        <div class="gkl-problem__outro">{{ section.settings.outro }}</div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "GK Gristle — problem",
  "tag": "section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_top_divider",
      "label": "Show top divider",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "eyebrow",
      "label": "Eyebrow",
      "default": "The Gristle Lowdown"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "The backline is… let's say questionable"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "body",
      "label": "Story",
      "default": "<p>When you're gigging as much as I do, you don't always get to play through your favorite amp. Sometimes you walk into a venue and the backline is… let's say questionable.</p><p>Or I'm sitting in with a friend's band in a high-profile situation, handed an amp I may not be that familiar with, and I need to know I'm gonna have my tone dialed.</p><p>Before I got this pedal, these situations may have caused me some angst. <strong>But no more.</strong></p><p>For the last 20+ years, I've kept one pedal in my bag that I know will always get me where I need to go — <strong>the Gristle King.</strong></p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "signature",
      "label": "Signature",
      "default": "— Greg Koch"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "image",
      "label": "Photo"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "caption",
      "label": "Photo caption",
      "default": "Greg Koch"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "outro",
      "label": "Outro",
      "default": "<p>Whether it's a tiny club with a dodgy combo or a big stage with a borrowed rig: plug in, get a decent clean sound on the amp, fire up the Gristle King, and the tone delivers <strong>unparalleled savagery</strong>.</p><p>My buddy and tone guru Tim Jauernig designed the Gristle King for me to solve a real problem — and it's never let me down.</p>"
    }
  ],
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "point",
      "name": "Point card",
      "limit": 4,
      "settings": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "icon",
          "label": "Tabler icon class",
          "default": "ti-wave-sine"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "title",
          "label": "Title",
          "default": "Amp-like overdrive"
        },
        {
          "type": "textarea",
          "id": "text",
          "label": "Text",
          "default": "A super dynamic, amp-like overdrive that sounds great at any volume."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "GK Gristle — problem",
      "blocks": [
        { "type": "point" },
        { "type": "point" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
